1.1 Split by subj

ggplot()+geom_smooth(data=prefdata,
                     aes(x = trial,
                         y = movedur,
                         color = factor(subj)))+
    facet_wrap(~factor(condition))+
  labs(title = 'Preferred')
## `geom_smooth()` using method = 'loess' and formula 'y ~ x'

ggplot()+geom_smooth(data=smalltdata,
                     aes(x = trial,
                         y = movedur,

    facet_wrap(~factor(condition))+
